channel.title: [show off] Kingdom Key from Kingdom Hearts[show off]
channel.description: I finally finished the kingdom key from the game Kindom Hearts, check it out and tell me what u think. I would be glad to post the model and ints but whatever i do, the models i make will show up as a strange object like stairs, a tree, pipe, ect. or it will show up invisible and no its not a polygon overflow and yes i did do "add model ####" for drop model and weild model.
